fulltitle: Rocio Lequio and Bruno Tombari – Embrujamiento
title: Rocio Lequio and Bruno Tombari – Embrujamiento

description:
Rocio Lequio and Bruno Tombari dance “Embrujamiento” by Ricardo Malerba, sung by Orlando Medina, at Nou Tango during the 1st Embrace Berlin Tango Festival 2014 in Berlin, Germany.
